		- api.bilibili.com
			( Comments are not displaying properly. Test: http://h.bilibili.com/dy\d+ )
		- data.bilibili.com
			( No functional breakage. Test: http://h.bilibili.com/dy\d+ or http://bml.bilibili.com/index2016/ )

	MCB:
		- app.bilibili.com
		- bangumi.bilibili.com
